title: The King of All Time Controls - Magnus Carlsen Wins Chess.com Speedchess Championship Finals!
description:
#agadmator Congratulations to @MagnusCarlsen who wins the #speedchess finals by an incredible margin: 18-9! Chess.com

Magnus Carlsen vs Hikaru Nakamura
Chess.com Speedchess Championship Finals 2018.
1+1,  2018, Jan-3
King's Indian Attack: Double Fianchetto Variation (A07)

1. Nf3 d5 2. g3 g6 3. Bg2 Bg7 4. O-O e5 5. d3 Ne7 6. e4 O-O 7. exd5 Nxd5 8. Re1 Nc6 9. Nc3 Nde7 10. Rb1 a5 11. a3 Re8 12. b4 axb4 13. axb4 Nf5 14. Bg5 f6 15. Bd2 Be6 16. b5 Nce7 17. g4 Nd4 18. Nxd4 Qxd4 19. Bxb7 Bxg4 20. Bf3 Bxf3 21. Qxf3 Ra3 22. b6 c6 23. Ne4 Nf5 24. Bb4 Ra2 25. Bc5 Qd7 26. Ra1 Rxc2 27. Ra7 Qd5 28. Rb1 Rxc5 29. b7 g5 30. b8=Q
